                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>16</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Activate this output when the transmission is not in neutral AND the switch is on
                                (Requires Automatic Transmission)
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
