        <para>
            <emph type="bold">Example:</emph>
            if you want the output to only come on when the vehicle transmission is in a reverse gear, you would set
            TEM_Aux1_Misc_Interlock_Param to 10 and TEM_Aux1_Gear_Interlock_Param to 125.
        </para>
