        <para>
            <emph type="boldundersc">WIRING INFORMATION</emph>
        </para>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>The wiring out of the pin labeled INTERLOCKED_SWITCH_AUX1_Output on the Brown 8-pin Remote Power
                    Module output connector is customer supplied
                </para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
        <figure id="f73000c9" figsize="pg-wide">
